    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Gap》讲述了主人公为治愈家族疾病，通过探索承载着珍贵记忆的平行现实而奋力挣扎的故事，这迫使他不断潜入意识深处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1458300/extras/f2da83611cb0729ab79c8d16e83e98e6.poster.avif?t=1768413923\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1458300/extras/f2da83611cb0729ab79c8d16e83e98e6.webm?t=1768413923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1458300/extras/f2da83611cb0729ab79c8d16e83e98e6.mp4?t=1768413923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神经科学家约书亚·海耶斯的家族罹患着逐渐侵蚀人类能力与心智的罕见神经障碍。通过他人生巅峰与低谷的视角，我们见证了这个家庭的挣扎与抗争。在探索原始极简空间的过程中，他不断邂逅通往过去记忆的物件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1458300/extras/63cb912216d5450a2bfed6f1d76ad417.poster.avif?t=1768413923\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1458300/extras/63cb912216d5450a2bfed6f1d76ad417.webm?t=1768413923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1458300/extras/63cb912216d5450a2bfed6f1d76ad417.mp4?t=1768413923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更甚的是，在参与由生物科技巨头Neuraxis主导的实验性神经科学项目时，约书亚不知不觉卷入企业阴谋的漩涡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为解开记忆迷网，他不得不直面这个令人不安的疑问——自己究竟能否被全然信任？</p>",
